/target
/target-wsl
**/*.rs.bk
*.stackdump
# Daemon runtime state (worktrees, captures) materialized by `rezidnt open` —
# never tracked, in this repo or an operator's. A spec with `repo = "."` opened
# from a repo dir writes it here; the spec-init e2e can leave one behind too.
.rezidnt/
# Guard: agents running host cargo with the WSL CARGO_TARGET_DIR=$HOME/.cache
# idiom create a colon-sanitized junk dir at the repo root (Git-Bash $HOME is
# C:\Users\...). Never track it.
/C*Usersdakot*
.cache/
